<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-2972] nodetool netstats progress does not update on receiving side</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2972</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;when you add/remove node to cluster, nodetool netstats show correct results only on sending side - on receiving side you can see only 0% progress&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12515826">CASSANDRA-2972</key>
            <summary>nodetool netstats progress does not update on receiving side</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
